Usage: setWhatIfLoadType [-help] <blackBoxCellName> -cell <cellName>
                         [-inputPin <libraryInputPin>] [-lib <libName>]
                         [-multiply_by <value>] [-port <inputPortName>]

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
<blackBoxCellName>              # name of the blackbox or blackblob cell
                                # (string, required)
-cell <cellName>                # Specifies the name of the cell from which the
                                # load value will be picked (string, required)
-inputPin <libraryInputPin>     # Specifies the input or inout pin of the cell 
                                # (string, optional)
-lib <libName>                  # Specifies the name of the timing library
                                # (string, optional)
-multiply_by <value>            # Specifies the load value multiplication
                                # factor (float, optional)
-port <inputPortName>           # Specifies the name of the input port
                                # (string, optional)